理準備"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"唔係個個都咁有吉士嘛，呢三次我開咪話比佢地聽，總有人好驚青咁問我點算，我都只能安慰佢地無事既（其實我都唔撚知點無事法⋯）<br />\n有d阿嬤走果時仲握住我隻手，叮囑我地小心唔好受傷，果下真係會想起過身了的先母⋯"},{"pid":"3022436c5a2afe03470274bd0fbc1cf72fdb0fc7","tid":1556471,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"aa0970210d390ade6056daa3fb820ea8b100557b","tid":1556471,"uid":57911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea418cd1954ecc8741641e2c20ddc96698726daf","tid":1556471,"uid":296715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b212939020b2b6b6c5573e4deab87c076b7b0bc","tid":1556471,"uid":57911,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"48534aa44461d8dfd0c224567431560d435b9ef0","tid":1556471,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:25:05.000Z","msg":"如果有footage,應該要多落街解釋<br />\n連登仔個個都明咩事，但中老年人唔會知件事全貌"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:27:04.000Z","msg":"啲濕鳩泛民KOL都不斷民意逆轉前民意逆轉後<br />\n搵人留言俾依班離地友聽叫佢哋出少句聲當幫忙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T09:04:38.000Z","msg":"七一後好似唔多見再講咩撚民意逆轉了，定我時運高睇唔到？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:29:42.000Z","msg":"YouTube啲泛民台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8afe903718b56ffcc9dd0577795545d8139cb3","tid":1556471,"uid":49216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T13:30:40.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}